# Token service errors (24000-24099)
E24000 = The grant_type is not supported.
E24001 = The client_id is required.
E24002 = An unexpected error occurred while looking up the authorization code.
E24003 = The authorization code was not found.
E24004 = The authorization code does not belong to the authenticated client.
E24005 = The authorization code is no longer valid.
E24006 = An unexpected error occurred while reading the authorization code.
E24007 = The redirect_uri does not match the authorization code.
E24008 = The code_verifier is required.
E24009 = An unexpected error occurred due to a data integrity issue.
E24010 = An unexpected error occurred while looking up the user.
E24011 = The user associated with the authorization code was not found.
E24012 = An unexpected error occurred while revoking the authorization code.
E24013 = An unexpected error occurred while looking up the refresh token.
E24014 = The refresh token was not found.
E24015 = The refresh token is no longer valid.
E24016 = An unexpected error occurred while reading the refresh token.
E24017 = The refresh token is missing the subject claim.
E24018 = The refresh token is missing the token_use claim.
E24019 = The refresh token type is invalid.
E24020 = The refresh token does not belong to the authenticated client.
E24021 = The refresh token subject is not a valid identifier.
E24022 = The user associated with the refresh token was not found.
E24023 = An unexpected error occurred while revoking the refresh token.
E24024 = An unexpected error occurred while loading signing keys.
E24025 = No signing key is available. Please contact your administrator.
E24026 = The client_id is not a valid identifier.
E24027 = The client was not found.
E24028 = An unexpected error occurred while looking up the client.
E24029 = An unexpected error occurred while looking up client credentials.
E24030 = The client credentials are invalid.
E24031 = Client authentication is required.
E24032 = The client assertion is missing the issuer claim.
E24033 = The client assertion is missing the subject claim.
E24034 = The client assertion issuer and subject must equal the client_id.
E24035 = The client assertion audience does not include the issuer.
E24036 = The client assertion has expired.
E24037 = The client assertion is not yet valid.
E24038 = The client assertion JWT header is invalid.
E24039 = The client assertion signature could not be verified.
E24040 = The client assertion algorithm is not supported.
E24041 = The client assertion key is invalid.
E24042 = The refresh token signature could not be verified.
E24043 = An unexpected error occurred while signing the access token.
E24044 = An unexpected error occurred while signing the ID token.
E24045 = An unexpected error occurred while signing the refresh token.
E24046 = An unexpected error occurred while saving the refresh token.
E24047 = An unexpected error occurred while saving the refresh token.
E24048 = The code_challenge_method is not supported.
E24049 = The code_verifier does not match the code_challenge.
